summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Unemployment rate, with a total of 21 data points.

Contrarily, the next significant trend is extremely increasing which exists from 2001 to 2005.
Also, the next significant trend is extremely increasing which exists from 2011 to 2014.
